### ==============================================================================
### VARIABLES GLOBALES DEL MÓDULO
### ==============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/apis/v1
@token = TU_JWT_TOKEN_AQUI
@idReserva = res_777888

### Crear una nueva reserva (Atómica con desglose de huéspedes acompañantes)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "hotel_id": "hot_paradisio_01",
    "room_type_id": "rt_suite_deluxe",
    "check_in": "2026-07-15",
    "check_out": "2026-07-20",
    "guests": [
        {
            "name": "Carlos Mendoza",
            "document": "DNI12345678",
            "is_primary": true
        },
        {
            "name": "Ana Silva",
            "document": "DNI87654321",
            "is_primary": false
        }
    ]
}

###

### Ver el historial cronológico de estancias/reservas del usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener la cadena interoperable BPI para dibujar el QR de pago en Flutter
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/qr/{{idReserva}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Simular confirmación bancaria (Acepta el pago, congela inventario y da estrellas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/verify/{{idReserva}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}